title: Redfish Storage Controller Battery
agents: agent_redfish
catalog: hw/server/redfish
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the battery status of Dell storage controllers via
 Redfish OEM data. It reports the primary status and RAID state of the
 controller battery.

discovery:
 One service is created for each storage controller that has Dell OEM battery data.

item:
 The ID of the storage controller.
